('Tropical Fire', 'tropical-fire', 'sativa', 24.3, 0.1, array['talkative', 'hungry', 'euphoric', 'tingly']::text[], array['cheese', 'skunk', 'herbal']::text[], array['caryophyllene', 'linalool', 'terpinolene']::text[], 'moderate', 10, '350-450 g/m²', '600-750 g/plant', 'Tropical Fire — A sativa prized for its energizing, cerebral lift that suits daytime creativity and social sessions. Expect cheese, skunk, herbal flavors with dominant caryophyllene, most often leaving users feeling talkative and hungry.'),
('Tropical Frost', 'tropical-frost', 'sativa', 16.5, 0.7, array['sleepy', 'relaxed', 'hungry', 'giggly']::text[], array['berry', 'citrus', 'skunk']::text[], array['caryophyllene', 'terpinolene', 'myrcene']::text[], 'moderate', 10, '425-525 g/m²', '600-750 g/plant', 'Tropical Frost — A sativa prized for its energizing, cerebral lift that suits daytime creativity and social sessions. Expect berry, citrus, skunk flavors with dominant caryophyllene, most often leaving users feeling sleepy and relaxed.'),
('Tropical Fuel', 'tropical-fuel', 'hybrid', 25.0, 0.6, array['relaxed', 'sleepy', 'focused', 'energetic', 'happy']::text[], array['mint', 'mango', 'woody']::text[], array['caryophyllene', 'pinene', 'linalool']::text[], 'hard', 10, '475-575 g/m²', '450-600 g/plant', 'Tropical Fuel — A balanced hybrid offering the best of both worlds — a smooth head high that settles into gentle body calm. Expect mint, mango, woody flavors with dominant caryophyllene, most often leaving users feeling relaxed and sleepy.')
